1
00:00:13,260 --> 00:00:15,620
(East Palace)

2
00:00:15,640 --> 00:00:16,230
Your Highness,

3
00:00:16,920 --> 00:00:17,960
you're finally awake.

4
00:00:18,464 --> 00:00:19,904
I was so afraid that you...

5
00:00:23,280 --> 00:00:25,030
I've returned safely, haven't I?

6
00:00:27,390 --> 00:00:28,550
Besides, my body

7
00:00:29,710 --> 00:00:31,000
is slowly getting better.

8
00:00:32,320 --> 00:00:33,790
But I clearly heard from our men

9
00:00:33,960 --> 00:00:34,750
that you almost...

10
00:00:35,320 --> 00:00:36,960
I just feel sorry for you,
Your Highness.

11
00:00:38,750 --> 00:00:41,280
Why didn't you tell
the Commandery Princess

12
00:00:41,310 --> 00:00:43,104
that you went
to find the cordyceps yourself?

13
00:00:47,560 --> 00:00:49,200
If she doesn't have feelings for me,

14
00:00:50,750 --> 00:00:51,750
even if she knew,

15
00:00:53,030 --> 00:00:55,640
she would just find another way
to repay the favor.

16
00:00:58,710 --> 00:01:00,110
Go tell her I'm back.

17
00:01:01,150 --> 00:01:02,390
I'll go see her tomorrow.

18
00:01:03,670 --> 00:01:04,920
But your health...

19
00:01:07,920 --> 00:01:08,870
I miss her.

20
00:01:23,020 --> 00:01:28,260
(Vibrant and Dazzling)

21
00:01:43,700 --> 00:01:46,660
(Vibrant and Dazzling)

22
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:03,040
Your Highness,

23
00:02:03,632 --> 00:02:04,832
what's wrong with you?

24
00:02:11,380 --> 00:02:19,060
(Vibrant and Dazzling)

25
00:02:37,080 --> 00:02:37,630
Your Highness.

26
00:02:39,920 --> 00:02:40,910
What's wrong with you?

27
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:46,030
I won't see her today.

28
00:04:18,300 --> 00:04:19,072
=Blossoms of Power=

29
00:04:19,072 --> 00:04:21,900
(Adapted from the novel, After My
Bloom, All Flowers Wither by Jin Huang)

30
00:04:21,980 --> 00:04:24,940
=Episode 9=

31
00:04:34,950 --> 00:04:36,160
From the look on your face,

32
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:37,870
is my condition

33
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:39,240
extremely bad?

34
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,680
Your Highness, the past ten years

35
00:04:42,070 --> 00:04:43,750
of excruciating pain you've endured

36
00:04:44,192 --> 00:04:45,390
have all been for nothing.

37
00:04:45,504 --> 00:04:47,950
You've returned to the time
when you were most deeply poisoned,

38
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,390
living on borrowed time.

39
00:04:50,190 --> 00:04:51,630
This relapse is severe.

40
00:04:51,630 --> 00:04:53,152
The poison can no longer be controlled.

41
00:04:54,160 --> 00:04:56,190
I can only temporarily
release some of the poison

42
00:04:56,270 --> 00:04:57,160
to alleviate it.

43
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:58,750
But your eyes

44
00:05:00,830 --> 00:05:02,510
can no longer distinguish colors.

45
00:05:10,190 --> 00:05:11,870
This is already
the best possible outcome.

46
00:05:14,870 --> 00:05:16,630
If we can't find an antidote,

47
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:18,720
your six senses will gradually fade.

48
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:20,160
After that,

49
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:22,240
your internal organs will fail.

50
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:24,630
How much time do I have left?

51
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:28,510
Five years at most.

52
00:05:29,024 --> 00:05:30,592
If you have another acute relapse,

53
00:05:32,496 --> 00:05:33,870
you'll only have three years left.

54
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:51,390
Tian Yuan.

55
00:05:55,160 --> 00:05:56,070
I was thinking,

56
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:58,800
since I only have
three to five years to live,

57
00:06:00,256 --> 00:06:02,510
I shouldn't get involved
with Commandery Princess anymore.

58
00:06:04,190 --> 00:06:04,800
Your Highness,

59
00:06:05,720 --> 00:06:06,870
we have three to five years.

60
00:06:07,070 --> 00:06:08,000
The world is vast.

61
00:06:08,510 --> 00:06:10,040
We can definitely find an antidote.

62
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:11,830
But I can't let her gamble with me.

63
00:06:16,510 --> 00:06:17,950
What if there's no hope?

64
00:06:18,752 --> 00:06:20,390
She's still in the prime of her life.

65
00:06:21,750 --> 00:06:23,160
She'd have to live a lonely life.

66
00:06:23,870 --> 00:06:25,120
How cruel would that be to her?

67
00:06:27,630 --> 00:06:28,270
Your Highness,

68
00:06:28,288 --> 00:06:30,288
Commandery Princess Zhaoning
requests an audience.

69
00:06:39,270 --> 00:06:39,950
I won't see her.

70
00:06:40,630 --> 00:06:41,190
Your Highness!

71
00:06:41,190 --> 00:06:42,790
From now on,
if Commandery Princess comes,

72
00:06:43,232 --> 00:06:45,040
I won't see her under any circumstances.

73
00:06:46,390 --> 00:06:46,870
Yes.

74
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,830
Did the Crown Prince really say that?

75
00:06:50,190 --> 00:06:50,870
Your Highness,

76
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:53,560
His Highness did say
he was already resting

77
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:54,680
and wouldn't see anyone.

78
00:06:58,510 --> 00:07:01,190
Please, help me give this box
of cold-warding incense to His Highness.

79
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:02,680
His Highness also instructed

80
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:04,510
that he won't accept any gifts either.

81
00:07:04,830 --> 00:07:06,510
Your Highness, please go back.

82
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:17,160
I always thought the Crown Prince
was so good to you.

83
00:07:17,310 --> 00:07:18,680
Who knew that when he turns cold,

84
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:19,720
he could be so arrogant?

85
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:22,240
Your Highness,

86
00:07:22,288 --> 00:07:23,968
let's go back to the Duke's Manor.

87
00:07:30,500 --> 00:07:33,860
(Contemplating the Pine Breeze)

88
00:07:33,904 --> 00:07:36,112
This is the medical record
of a close friend of mine.

89
00:07:36,144 --> 00:07:38,352
I'd like to ask you to take a look
for me, Physician Xie.

90
00:07:38,384 --> 00:07:39,408
Is he in good health?

91
00:07:50,310 --> 00:07:51,720
This person's body is weak.

92
00:07:51,968 --> 00:07:53,360
He has been ill for a long time.

93
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:56,000
And based on the medical record,

94
00:07:56,510 --> 00:07:57,830
his old illness has relapsed.

95
00:07:58,120 --> 00:07:58,800
His eyes

96
00:07:58,976 --> 00:08:00,448
can no longer distinguish colors.

97
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:02,600
His eyes

98
00:08:03,190 --> 00:08:04,360
can't see colors?

99
00:08:04,360 --> 00:08:05,920
This is just a superficial symptom.

100
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:08,190
His lifespan...

101
00:08:09,750 --> 00:08:11,360
He only has three to five years left.

102
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:13,480
Are you sure?

103
00:08:14,070 --> 00:08:15,510
If he is your dear friend,

104
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:17,600
then you should

105
00:08:17,950 --> 00:08:19,750
show him more care and concern.

106
00:08:42,630 --> 00:08:43,360
Your Highness.

107
00:08:44,910 --> 00:08:45,910
It's so late.

108
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:47,150
Why are you still awake?

109
00:08:47,536 --> 00:08:48,976
I was just thinking about some things.

110
00:08:49,550 --> 00:08:50,750
About

111
00:08:51,630 --> 00:08:52,750
the Crown Prince?

112
00:08:54,800 --> 00:08:56,840
His Highness has been recuperating
in a Taoist temple for a long time.

113
00:08:56,840 --> 00:08:58,672
He's long past the age
for his coming-of-age ceremony.

114
00:08:58,750 --> 00:08:59,750
In half a month,

115
00:08:59,750 --> 00:09:01,380
His Majesty will hold the ceremony
for him.

116
00:09:01,390 --> 00:09:03,840
The Ministry of Rites and the Court
of Imperial Clan Affairs have been busy.

117
00:09:03,910 --> 00:09:05,088
It's going to be a grand event.

118
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:08,510
I always suspected that the person
behind the Tagara Incense,

119
00:09:08,512 --> 00:09:10,670
who could command Cui Jinbai
and the Embroidered Envoy

120
00:09:11,150 --> 00:09:12,600
might be one of the princes.

121
00:09:13,390 --> 00:09:16,480
But now it seems, Crown Prince is frail
and has been ill for a long time.

122
00:09:16,560 --> 00:09:18,400
It's impossible for him
to know martial arts.

123
00:09:18,464 --> 00:09:20,144
If he is truly destined
for a short life,

124
00:09:20,192 --> 00:09:22,224
he wouldn't be obsessed
with power struggles.

125
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:23,480
He and I

126
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:25,080
wouldn't become enemies

127
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:26,432
due to a change in our positions.

128
00:09:26,670 --> 00:09:28,200
Are you saying

129
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:31,240
you've decided
to marry Crown Prince?

130
00:09:32,790 --> 00:09:33,750
If he agrees,

131
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:35,664
I will form an alliance
with the East Palace.

132
00:09:36,150 --> 00:09:37,390
Three to five years

133
00:09:37,390 --> 00:09:38,850
is enough time to lay the groundwork,

134
00:09:39,030 --> 00:09:40,200
appoint capable officials,

135
00:09:40,550 --> 00:09:41,670
ensure stability in northwest

136
00:09:42,240 --> 00:09:43,600
and protect the Duke of Wei's Manor.

137
00:09:43,910 --> 00:09:45,670
I can also secure a peaceful life
for myself.

138
00:09:47,270 --> 00:09:48,270
In exchange,

139
00:09:48,280 --> 00:09:51,184
I'll do everything in my power to help
him find the person who poisoned him.

140
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:52,870
The Crown Prince and I

141
00:09:53,030 --> 00:09:54,440
will get along like family.

142
00:09:58,150 --> 00:09:59,630
Cure my eye condition?

143
00:10:00,510 --> 00:10:01,480
Physician Xie said

144
00:10:01,504 --> 00:10:03,744
that Commandery Princess
is completely devoted to you.

145
00:10:03,840 --> 00:10:05,712
She's frantically searching
for a prescription

146
00:10:05,712 --> 00:10:07,910
and a cure for your color blindness.

147
00:10:10,288 --> 00:10:11,630
Is what you're saying true?

148
00:10:11,910 --> 00:10:12,510
It's true.

149
00:10:13,584 --> 00:10:15,080
She sent a letter in her own hand,

150
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:16,990
inviting Hua Fuhai
to discuss an important matter.

151
00:10:17,072 --> 00:10:17,616
Your Highness,

152
00:10:17,790 --> 00:10:19,790
you should go see her as Hua Fuhai.

153
00:10:19,790 --> 00:10:21,700
That way, you can understand
her true intentions.

154
00:10:21,710 --> 00:10:24,980
(I have an important matter to discuss.
Meet me at Weiyu Tower. Shen Xihe.)

155
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:34,270
Greetings, Your Highness.

156
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:36,720
Please have a seat, sir.

157
00:10:38,080 --> 00:10:39,080
Thank you, Your Highness.

158
00:10:45,536 --> 00:10:47,920
I'd like to ask for your help
with something, Young Master Hua.

159
00:10:48,150 --> 00:10:49,550
Please, just tell me what you need.

160
00:10:49,910 --> 00:10:51,360
You have friends all over the world.

161
00:10:51,510 --> 00:10:53,030
Could you help me find out

162
00:10:53,150 --> 00:10:55,910
where I can find the wild bees
that can cure an eye condition?

163
00:10:58,870 --> 00:11:02,080
I also saw the imperial notice posted
by His Majesty seeking a cure.

164
00:11:03,030 --> 00:11:04,270
Forgive me for asking,

165
00:11:04,640 --> 00:11:05,910
but are you seeking this cure

166
00:11:06,750 --> 00:11:08,240
for the Crown Prince of the East Palace?

167
00:11:09,360 --> 00:11:09,960
Yes.

168
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:15,150
And how do you propose

169
00:11:15,150 --> 00:11:16,656
to conduct this transaction with me?

170
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:18,320
I can promise you

171
00:11:18,480 --> 00:11:19,600
the markets of northwest.

172
00:11:22,360 --> 00:11:24,270
The horses, cattle,
and sheep of northwest,

173
00:11:24,270 --> 00:11:25,440
as well as its silk and jade,

174
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:27,790
are what every merchant dreams of.

175
00:11:28,510 --> 00:11:30,600
Every single one is a source
of immense profit.

176
00:11:32,200 --> 00:11:33,390
Your Highness, could it be

177
00:11:34,030 --> 00:11:35,670
that you are in love
with the Crown Prince?

178
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:38,510
In my heart,

179
00:11:39,390 --> 00:11:40,870
no one can compare to him.

180
00:11:43,510 --> 00:11:44,910
But the rumors say

181
00:11:45,536 --> 00:11:47,392
the Crown Prince is destined
for a short life.

182
00:11:49,670 --> 00:11:52,790
People always measure a marriage
by its length.

183
00:11:53,870 --> 00:11:54,910
But they don't realize

184
00:11:55,080 --> 00:11:57,720
that a resentful couple can spend
decades together under one roof,

185
00:11:58,160 --> 00:12:00,624
their hearts wearing each other down
until they become strangers,

186
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:03,080
the fire in their hearts
fading like a dying lamp.

187
00:12:03,790 --> 00:12:05,550
If a union is true,

188
00:12:06,320 --> 00:12:08,368
then even if it's as brief
as the morning dew,

189
00:12:08,528 --> 00:12:11,952
it's better than a hundred years of
empty entanglement like a withered vine.

190
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:18,480
A single night of true love

191
00:12:18,960 --> 00:12:20,150
is worth more than an eternity.

192
00:12:30,150 --> 00:12:31,550
You have been so sincere

193
00:12:31,728 --> 00:12:33,000
and your promise is so generous.

194
00:12:33,910 --> 00:12:36,240
I will certainly do everything
in my power to help.

195
00:12:53,910 --> 00:12:54,960
Xihe,

196
00:12:55,960 --> 00:12:58,840
you've been in the imperial capital
for some time now.

197
00:12:59,390 --> 00:13:01,480
Which prince have you chosen

198
00:13:01,480 --> 00:13:02,600
to be your husband?

199
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:04,320
Your Majesty's princes

200
00:13:04,320 --> 00:13:05,600
are all exceptional men.

201
00:13:06,240 --> 00:13:07,320
But I

202
00:13:07,750 --> 00:13:09,390
only have eyes for the Crown Prince.

203
00:13:13,960 --> 00:13:15,200
These past few days,

204
00:13:15,840 --> 00:13:17,390
you haven't smiled

205
00:13:17,390 --> 00:13:18,840
at any of the other princes.

206
00:13:18,896 --> 00:13:20,784
Instead, you've been going
to the East Palace

207
00:13:20,816 --> 00:13:21,856
quite frequently.

208
00:13:22,630 --> 00:13:23,790
However,

209
00:13:24,080 --> 00:13:25,480
you should be aware

210
00:13:25,910 --> 00:13:27,750
of the Crown Prince's
frail constitution.

211
00:13:27,870 --> 00:13:30,270
I admire His Highness's
character and talent.

212
00:13:30,848 --> 00:13:33,710
A spiritual connection is more important
than spending a lifetime together.

213
00:13:33,720 --> 00:13:35,510
I only wish for us
to live in mutual respect,

214
00:13:35,520 --> 00:13:37,270
supporting each other
through thick and thin,

215
00:13:37,270 --> 00:13:38,816
and create a beautiful story together.

216
00:13:39,480 --> 00:13:40,750
Very well.

217
00:13:41,670 --> 00:13:42,670
However,

218
00:13:43,000 --> 00:13:45,320
I know what your father wants.

219
00:13:46,150 --> 00:13:49,440
Your father wishes for you
to marry the Ninth Prince, Prince Lie.

220
00:13:49,870 --> 00:13:51,600
My marriage is my own affair.

221
00:13:52,080 --> 00:13:54,790
The Crown Prince is also my own choice.

222
00:13:58,120 --> 00:14:01,390
Huayong is my most beloved son.

223
00:14:01,790 --> 00:14:03,200
Since you admire him,

224
00:14:03,200 --> 00:14:04,510
I am very pleased.

225
00:14:05,360 --> 00:14:06,320
I think

226
00:14:06,670 --> 00:14:08,960
we should wait
until his health improves a bit.

227
00:14:09,360 --> 00:14:10,030
Then I

228
00:14:10,550 --> 00:14:12,150
will ask for his opinion.

229
00:14:12,288 --> 00:14:13,960
We can make a final decision after that.

230
00:14:14,440 --> 00:14:15,720
As for your father,

231
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:17,910
I will inform him beforehand.

232
00:14:18,630 --> 00:14:19,550
Thank you, Your Majesty.

233
00:14:29,080 --> 00:14:29,670
Your Highness.

234
00:14:30,080 --> 00:14:32,080
I have been by your side
since I was a child,

235
00:14:32,440 --> 00:14:34,510
and I have never seen you
so deeply troubled.

236
00:14:35,270 --> 00:14:36,120
Today,

237
00:14:37,216 --> 00:14:39,240
Commandery Princess went
to see His Majesty.

238
00:14:40,720 --> 00:14:42,390
She said that among all the princes,

239
00:14:45,750 --> 00:14:47,120
she only has feelings for me.

240
00:14:47,670 --> 00:14:49,270
Then what did she say

241
00:14:49,792 --> 00:14:51,584
when you were disguised as Hua Fuhai?

242
00:14:52,670 --> 00:14:53,600
She said,

243
00:14:54,432 --> 00:14:56,120
"Even if it's as brief
as the morning dew,

244
00:14:56,400 --> 00:14:59,290
it's better than a hundred years of
empty entanglement like a withered vine.

245
00:15:00,630 --> 00:15:01,790
A single night of true love

246
00:15:02,160 --> 00:15:03,670
is worth more than an eternity."

247
00:15:04,320 --> 00:15:04,870
Your Highness,

248
00:15:05,390 --> 00:15:06,000
you see,

249
00:15:06,320 --> 00:15:07,390
in her eyes,

250
00:15:07,910 --> 00:15:09,120
mutual affection

251
00:15:09,136 --> 00:15:11,248
is more important
than spending every day together.

252
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:20,840
She may not care about
how long I have to live,

253
00:15:22,840 --> 00:15:24,600
but I must consider her future.

254
00:15:27,030 --> 00:15:27,670
Your Highness,

255
00:15:28,320 --> 00:15:29,360
if you truly care for her,

256
00:15:29,680 --> 00:15:32,000
you shouldn't be so indifferent
about life and death.

257
00:15:32,368 --> 00:15:34,480
Now that the other princes
are out of the running,

258
00:15:34,720 --> 00:15:36,320
you are her future husband.

259
00:15:36,670 --> 00:15:37,910
You must pull yourself together,

260
00:15:38,030 --> 00:15:39,150
find an antidote,

261
00:15:39,670 --> 00:15:41,440
and grow old with her.

262
00:15:53,660 --> 00:15:57,260
(Prince Xin's Manor)

263
00:16:14,000 --> 00:16:14,870
Changqing,

264
00:16:15,440 --> 00:16:16,670
I still can't get over her.

265
00:16:18,550 --> 00:16:20,030
I can't even bear to hear her name

266
00:16:21,510 --> 00:16:23,080
mentioned alongside someone else's.

267
00:16:23,510 --> 00:16:25,360
Even if she wants
to marry the Crown Prince,

268
00:16:26,360 --> 00:16:27,550
it's not for love.

269
00:16:31,104 --> 00:16:32,320
What do you mean, Changqing?

270
00:16:33,240 --> 00:16:35,320
Although Shen Xihe
often visits the East Palace,

271
00:16:36,240 --> 00:16:37,870
I have never seen

272
00:16:39,120 --> 00:16:40,630
any love for Huayong in her eyes.

273
00:16:41,750 --> 00:16:43,510
If a marriage isn't for love,

274
00:16:43,568 --> 00:16:45,000
then it must be for personal gain.

275
00:16:45,360 --> 00:16:46,080
Personal gain?

276
00:16:48,200 --> 00:16:49,790
Huayong has always been frail
and sickly.

277
00:16:50,080 --> 00:16:51,232
If something were to happen...

278
00:16:55,168 --> 00:16:57,728
Who would protect northwest for
Commandery Princess in the future?

279
00:16:57,910 --> 00:16:59,270
As a former Crown Princess,

280
00:16:59,630 --> 00:17:01,360
which new emperor would tolerate her?

281
00:17:03,960 --> 00:17:05,510
Don't underestimate ladies.

282
00:17:06,240 --> 00:17:08,110
A lady is also capable
of overturning the world.

283
00:17:08,510 --> 00:17:09,790
The harem has no empress.

284
00:17:10,310 --> 00:17:12,352
It would be perfectly reasonable
for Shen Xihe

285
00:17:12,384 --> 00:17:14,400
to manage the six palaces
as the Crown Princess.

286
00:17:15,000 --> 00:17:16,480
At that time, the entire harem

287
00:17:16,960 --> 00:17:18,400
would fall into her hands.

288
00:17:19,510 --> 00:17:20,960
Her father is the Duke of Wei.

289
00:17:21,030 --> 00:17:22,864
Her maternal grandfather
is the Grand Censor.

290
00:17:22,912 --> 00:17:25,472
She is also on good terms
with the heir of the Marquis of Shunan.

291
00:17:25,552 --> 00:17:27,160
Any scheme of hers

292
00:17:27,680 --> 00:17:29,400
is not just a fantasy.

293
00:17:32,960 --> 00:17:34,680
If this path succeeds,

294
00:17:34,750 --> 00:17:36,608
northwest will have
nothing to worry about.

295
00:17:37,160 --> 00:17:38,480
The Shen family

296
00:17:39,000 --> 00:17:40,400
will become truly unshakable.

297
00:17:47,030 --> 00:17:48,200
So that's it.

298
00:17:51,550 --> 00:17:52,750
So this is where I lost.

299
00:17:55,790 --> 00:17:56,750
Changying,

300
00:17:58,920 --> 00:18:01,310
if Shen Xihe's intentions
are truly as I suspect,

301
00:18:02,480 --> 00:18:04,200
then you rushing to her side recklessly

302
00:18:04,590 --> 00:18:06,270
is just like a moth to a flame.

303
00:18:25,440 --> 00:18:26,550
Greetings, Your Highness.

304
00:18:26,688 --> 00:18:29,200
I had you thoroughly investigate
Commandery Princess Zhaoning.

305
00:18:29,680 --> 00:18:31,000
Did you find anything unusual?

306
00:18:31,550 --> 00:18:33,880
Commandery Princess Zhaoning
did indeed grow up in northwest.

307
00:18:34,200 --> 00:18:35,480
There is only one peculiar matter.

308
00:18:35,830 --> 00:18:36,400
Speak.

309
00:18:36,464 --> 00:18:38,550
On her journey from northwest
to the imperial capital,

310
00:18:38,608 --> 00:18:40,430
she was passing
through Lingxiang County by boat

311
00:18:40,440 --> 00:18:41,552
when she fell into the river.

312
00:18:41,560 --> 00:18:42,590
She nearly lost her life.

313
00:18:42,736 --> 00:18:44,160
The Observatory Official also said

314
00:18:44,270 --> 00:18:45,440
that on that day,
two moons appeared in the sky.

315
00:18:45,440 --> 00:18:46,608
The star gate opened wide.

316
00:18:46,640 --> 00:18:47,856
It was a celestial anomaly.

317
00:18:52,200 --> 00:18:54,000
Two moons in the sky?

318
00:18:56,270 --> 00:18:57,830
The star gate opened wide...

319
00:19:19,780 --> 00:19:22,380
(Gu Qingshu, the Gu's Second Daughter)
Brother-in-law.

320
00:19:31,310 --> 00:19:32,070
Brother-in-law.

321
00:19:34,720 --> 00:19:36,240
Didn't I tell you?

322
00:19:36,864 --> 00:19:38,550
Don't stay cooped up
in the manor all day.

323
00:19:39,088 --> 00:19:40,350
Go out for a walk more often.

324
00:19:41,720 --> 00:19:43,510
I've arranged for guards
around the manor.

325
00:19:43,960 --> 00:19:45,160
You don't have to worry at all.

326
00:19:47,000 --> 00:19:49,328
Three years ago, when
the Gu family fell into misfortune,

327
00:19:49,488 --> 00:19:51,300
you risked the crime
of deceiving the emperor,

328
00:19:51,344 --> 00:19:52,880
falsely claiming I had died of illness

329
00:19:52,912 --> 00:19:53,790
to save me.

330
00:19:54,590 --> 00:19:56,440
I don't want to appear before the world

331
00:19:56,830 --> 00:19:58,160
for fear of causing you trouble.

332
00:20:02,880 --> 00:20:04,000
I never intended

333
00:20:04,592 --> 00:20:06,592
for you to hide
for the rest of your life.

334
00:20:07,000 --> 00:20:07,960
This time,

335
00:20:08,000 --> 00:20:09,904
from among the talented men
selected by the court,

336
00:20:10,400 --> 00:20:11,680
I will choose a reliable young man

337
00:20:12,000 --> 00:20:13,590
and arrange a good marriage for you.

338
00:20:14,240 --> 00:20:15,590
Once you leave the imperial capital

339
00:20:15,590 --> 00:20:16,550
and change your name,

340
00:20:16,960 --> 00:20:18,350
the world is vast,

341
00:20:18,496 --> 00:20:19,968
and you'll have no more worries.

342
00:20:21,920 --> 00:20:22,480
Shu,

343
00:20:22,960 --> 00:20:24,160
I came today

344
00:20:24,170 --> 00:20:25,632
because I wanted to ask you something.

345
00:20:26,310 --> 00:20:27,270
Did your older sister

346
00:20:28,070 --> 00:20:30,960
have any connection
with Commandery Princess Zhaoning,

347
00:20:32,544 --> 00:20:34,000
the Duke of Wei's daughter?

348
00:20:34,384 --> 00:20:35,750
One was in the imperial capital,

349
00:20:36,240 --> 00:20:37,310
the other in northwest.

350
00:20:37,488 --> 00:20:39,312
How could they have known each other?

351
00:20:45,104 --> 00:20:47,240
It's been three years
since my sister passed away.

352
00:20:48,350 --> 00:20:50,640
Why are you still asking about her past?

353
00:20:51,750 --> 00:20:52,550
Brother-in-law,

354
00:20:54,270 --> 00:20:55,720
since I moved into this manor,

355
00:20:56,160 --> 00:20:57,550
you've only visited me three times.

356
00:20:59,160 --> 00:20:59,960
The first time,

357
00:21:00,192 --> 00:21:02,240
you asked if I had any
of my sister's belongings.

358
00:21:03,000 --> 00:21:03,790
The second time,

359
00:21:04,432 --> 00:21:06,528
you took me to pay respects
at my sister's grave.

360
00:21:06,790 --> 00:21:08,200
The third time is today.

361
00:21:08,960 --> 00:21:10,912
And again,
you're asking about my sister.

362
00:21:13,550 --> 00:21:15,160
My sister never loved you.

363
00:21:15,750 --> 00:21:16,680
But in your eyes,

364
00:21:17,750 --> 00:21:19,160
you still can't see anyone else.

365
00:21:21,680 --> 00:21:23,110
Heaven gave me

366
00:21:24,680 --> 00:21:26,510
too little time with your sister.

367
00:21:27,750 --> 00:21:29,200
If I were given another chance

368
00:21:30,240 --> 00:21:31,880
to start over,

369
00:21:33,270 --> 00:21:34,680
I would surely

370
00:21:35,640 --> 00:21:36,880
love her for a lifetime.

371
00:21:38,880 --> 00:21:40,640
I would never let her leave me again.

372
00:22:00,350 --> 00:22:01,200
Brother-in-law,

373
00:22:02,384 --> 00:22:03,760
why can't you take a good look

374
00:22:04,680 --> 00:22:06,480
at the people who are still alive?

375
00:22:26,880 --> 00:22:29,590
Xihe, you look so refreshed
and full of energy.

376
00:22:29,680 --> 00:22:31,520
It's like you're a completely
different person.

377
00:22:32,070 --> 00:22:33,830
Did you take some kind
of miracle medicine?

378
00:22:43,680 --> 00:22:45,680
This flirtatious scoundrel

379
00:22:46,830 --> 00:22:48,350
should be caught and taught a lesson.

380
00:22:52,270 --> 00:22:53,310
Once you're settled,

381
00:22:53,310 --> 00:22:54,540
I'll take you to see the stables.

382
00:22:54,550 --> 00:22:55,030
Okay.

383
00:22:56,240 --> 00:22:56,880
Du Huo.

384
00:22:58,240 --> 00:22:58,880
Du Huo.

385
00:22:59,070 --> 00:22:59,680
Du Huo.

386
00:23:02,832 --> 00:23:05,184
Your Highness,
it's the Commandery Princess's cat.

387
00:23:12,200 --> 00:23:12,750
Thank you.

388
00:23:12,944 --> 00:23:15,392
My cat has offended you.
Please forgive me, Your Highness.

389
00:23:16,680 --> 00:23:17,270
It's fine.

390
00:23:25,240 --> 00:23:27,240
In that case, I shall take my leave.

391
00:23:47,160 --> 00:23:47,880
Mo Yu,

392
00:23:48,270 --> 00:23:49,400
go get two sachets.

393
00:23:49,536 --> 00:23:51,400
One to repel insects
and one to repel snakes.

394
00:23:51,504 --> 00:23:53,590
Have Tian Yuan hang them
in the Crown Prince's room.

395
00:23:53,750 --> 00:23:55,720
The Crown Prince is so indifferent,

396
00:23:56,110 --> 00:23:57,440
yet you still care so much.

397
00:23:59,270 --> 00:24:00,400
I have already chosen him.

398
00:24:01,240 --> 00:24:02,030
Your Highness,

399
00:24:02,480 --> 00:24:04,680
I always thought most highly
of the Crown Prince before.

400
00:24:04,790 --> 00:24:06,160
But this time, it's confirmed.

401
00:24:06,640 --> 00:24:08,350
The poison in his body
is quite peculiar.

402
00:24:08,480 --> 00:24:10,830
Even if it's suppressed for a while,
it will recur.

403
00:24:11,160 --> 00:24:13,104
Moreover, he's been eroded
by the poison for years.

404
00:24:13,120 --> 00:24:14,920
His internal organs are extremely weak.

405
00:24:15,030 --> 00:24:16,336
He truly won't live a long life.

406
00:24:16,680 --> 00:24:18,880
Are you really going
to tell the Duke and your brother

407
00:24:18,890 --> 00:24:20,720
that you're going
to marry Crown Prince?

408
00:24:22,110 --> 00:24:23,310
This marriage

409
00:24:23,488 --> 00:24:24,790
has nothing to do with love.

410
00:24:26,030 --> 00:24:28,030
It's about choosing an ally.

411
00:24:29,350 --> 00:24:30,640
Someone with little time left

412
00:24:31,510 --> 00:24:33,030
and no ability to fight back

413
00:24:33,680 --> 00:24:34,830
is exactly what I need.

414
00:24:56,110 --> 00:24:56,640
Your Highness,

415
00:24:57,310 --> 00:24:59,350
what if there's some misunderstanding
in all this?

416
00:25:00,030 --> 00:25:01,880
Commandery Princess favors you
and you alone.

417
00:25:02,016 --> 00:25:03,504
She checked your medical records,

418
00:25:03,536 --> 00:25:05,344
and sought out physicians
and medicine for you.

419
00:25:05,510 --> 00:25:06,510
Her concern for you

420
00:25:06,960 --> 00:25:08,270
is something even I can feel.

421
00:25:09,830 --> 00:25:10,400
Is that so?

422
00:25:14,590 --> 00:25:15,920
Could it be that she chose me

423
00:25:18,800 --> 00:25:20,440
for any other reason than my short life?

424
00:25:22,240 --> 00:25:22,830
But...

425
00:25:24,110 --> 00:25:25,590
When you're with her,

426
00:25:25,728 --> 00:25:27,270
it's like you become a different person.

427
00:25:27,790 --> 00:25:29,110
You even laugh a lot more.

428
00:25:29,744 --> 00:25:31,840
You no longer seem indifferent
to life and death.

429
00:25:32,030 --> 00:25:34,000
You have the will to live,
to fight to stay alive.

430
00:25:34,720 --> 00:25:35,750
Rather than letting go,

431
00:25:36,160 --> 00:25:38,790
I would rather see you
become happy and bright.

432
00:25:51,750 --> 00:25:52,350
Your Highness!

433
00:26:03,240 --> 00:26:03,790
Your Highness,

434
00:26:03,824 --> 00:26:05,072
Commandery Princess was here.

435
00:26:05,080 --> 00:26:06,270
When she heard you were asleep,

436
00:26:06,510 --> 00:26:07,400
she left.

437
00:26:12,400 --> 00:26:13,550
Did she say anything else?

438
00:26:13,880 --> 00:26:14,750
She asked

439
00:26:15,000 --> 00:26:16,070
if you were ill again

440
00:26:16,790 --> 00:26:17,720
and if it was serious.

441
00:26:22,640 --> 00:26:23,350
Then...

442
00:26:23,790 --> 00:26:24,400
Your Highness,

443
00:26:24,640 --> 00:26:25,920
about your marriage to her...

444
00:26:36,920 --> 00:26:38,720
Seeing your complexion
improve day by day,

445
00:26:38,720 --> 00:26:39,440
in the future,

446
00:26:39,550 --> 00:26:41,248
we'll surely be able
to ride together often.

447
00:26:41,312 --> 00:26:42,160
In a little while,

448
00:26:42,480 --> 00:26:43,400
I should be able to.

449
00:26:49,310 --> 00:26:50,110
Young Master Bu,

450
00:26:50,720 --> 00:26:51,920
there's something I want.

451
00:27:00,640 --> 00:27:02,240
I can certainly give that a try.

452
00:27:02,880 --> 00:27:03,680
Xihe,

453
00:27:04,030 --> 00:27:05,680
wait for me to bring it back for you.

454
00:27:19,480 --> 00:27:21,056
Fourth Sister, what are you doing?

455
00:27:21,080 --> 00:27:23,720
So what? Commandery Princess Zhaoning
grew up in the northwest.

456
00:27:23,830 --> 00:27:26,200
Every lady from the northwest
knows how to ride.

457
00:27:26,680 --> 00:27:27,400
Today,

458
00:27:27,590 --> 00:27:28,960
let us see for ourselves.

459
00:27:45,600 --> 00:27:47,000
Your Highness, Commandery Princess...

460
00:27:47,000 --> 00:27:48,110
I don't want to hear it.

461
00:27:48,110 --> 00:27:49,540
Commandery Princess
fell from her horse into a ravine.

462
00:27:49,550 --> 00:27:51,480
Noble Consort Rong,
afraid of alarming His Majesty,

463
00:27:51,490 --> 00:27:52,272
has blocked the news.

464
00:27:52,288 --> 00:27:54,850
Young Master Bu and his guards
have been searching for a long time,

465
00:27:54,864 --> 00:27:55,850
but she remains missing.

466
00:27:55,920 --> 00:27:56,944
Take me there, quickly.

467
00:28:15,070 --> 00:28:15,640
Your Highness,

468
00:28:16,496 --> 00:28:17,952
the Commandery Princess...

469
00:28:26,608 --> 00:28:28,704
Xihe would never just sit
and wait for death.

470
00:28:45,110 --> 00:28:46,512
Tian Yuan, follow the mountain path

471
00:28:46,528 --> 00:28:47,950
and search at the bottom of the cliff.

472
00:28:47,960 --> 00:28:48,350
Okay.

473
00:29:28,400 --> 00:29:29,000
Your Highness,

474
00:29:29,070 --> 00:29:31,340
Commandery Princess Zhaoning
fell off a cliff while riding.

475
00:29:31,350 --> 00:29:32,070
What did you say?

476
00:29:33,480 --> 00:29:34,400
Take me to her, quickly!

477
00:29:34,590 --> 00:29:35,030
Yes.

478
00:29:35,510 --> 00:29:36,160
Changying!

479
00:29:39,160 --> 00:29:39,960
Xihe!

480
00:31:26,350 --> 00:31:27,110
(This scent...)

481
00:31:38,480 --> 00:31:39,200
Xihe!

482
00:31:49,010 --> 00:31:54,720
♪Let it all go,
give my tears to the flowers♪

483
00:31:56,160 --> 00:32:02,060
♪Beneath my feet,
eternal doom is more than wind and sand♪

484
00:32:03,140 --> 00:32:08,730
♪That perfectly plotted love hides
in the clamor♪

485
00:32:10,180 --> 00:32:15,680
♪Between us,
it's both treacherous and flawless♪

486
00:32:17,060 --> 00:32:22,590
♪I want destiny,
and also tender words of love♪

487
00:32:22,990 --> 00:32:30,740
♪As night stains my eyes,
I'll gaze once more at the rosy clouds♪

488
00:32:30,990 --> 00:32:34,370
♪I have a dream
of a long wind in my sleeves♪

489
00:32:34,570 --> 00:32:37,930
♪My heart rises and falls,
we embrace in a sea of clouds♪

490
00:32:38,130 --> 00:32:41,470
♪In this eternity, you are a part of it♪

491
00:32:41,470 --> 00:32:45,060
♪My longing can level mountains
and cross countless waters♪

492
00:32:45,060 --> 00:32:48,330
♪Drunk or sober, it's all like a dream♪

493
00:32:48,470 --> 00:32:52,020
♪Stars sink into my hair,
the moon slips through my fingers♪

494
00:32:52,020 --> 00:32:55,590
♪For how much joy
do we share this life together♪

495
00:32:55,590 --> 00:33:02,040
♪Withering and flourishing,
year after year♪

496
00:33:02,460 --> 00:33:05,850
♪I have a dream
of a long wind in my sleeves♪

497
00:33:05,850 --> 00:33:09,510
♪My heart rises and falls,
we embrace in a sea of clouds♪

498
00:33:09,510 --> 00:33:12,940
♪In this eternity, you are a part of it♪

499
00:33:12,940 --> 00:33:16,480
♪My longing can level mountains
and cross countless rivers♪

500
00:33:16,480 --> 00:33:19,730
♪Drunk or sober, it's all like a dream♪

501
00:33:19,940 --> 00:33:23,410
♪Stars sink into my hair,
the moon slips through my fingers♪

502
00:33:23,410 --> 00:33:26,950
♪For how much joy
do we share this life together♪

503
00:33:26,950 --> 00:33:30,110
♪Withering and flourishing,
year after year♪

504
00:33:35,600 --> 00:33:37,690
♪May the sand and dirt in my sleeves♪

505
00:33:37,930 --> 00:33:40,930
♪Become the tears
in the corner of my eyes♪

506
00:33:41,480 --> 00:33:43,770
♪And blossom into a flower♪

507
00:34:03,392 --> 00:34:04,480
The fever's finally gone.

508
00:34:09,510 --> 00:34:10,670
You saved me.

509
00:34:22,710 --> 00:34:23,710
It was a coincidence.

510
00:34:27,472 --> 00:34:29,776
Thank you for saving my life today,
Your Highness.

511
00:34:30,550 --> 00:34:31,880
I will remember this.

512
00:34:32,440 --> 00:34:33,440
In the future,

513
00:34:33,510 --> 00:34:35,230
if I have the chance
to give my life for you,

514
00:34:36,150 --> 00:34:37,960
I will not hesitate for a moment.

515
00:34:43,568 --> 00:34:45,120
You don't need to give your life.

516
00:34:46,400 --> 00:34:47,800
If you truly wish to repay me,

517
00:34:48,000 --> 00:34:49,630
how about you answer a question
for me now?

518
00:34:51,280 --> 00:34:52,230
What question?

519
00:34:53,280 --> 00:34:54,550
I wonder if you would be

520
00:34:55,872 --> 00:34:57,008
willing to marry me.

521
00:35:03,360 --> 00:35:04,760
All the princes

522
00:35:04,920 --> 00:35:05,960
have their own merits.

523
00:35:06,230 --> 00:35:07,400
They are all vying for my hand.

524
00:35:07,920 --> 00:35:10,280
What gives you the advantage,
Your Highness?

525
00:35:18,110 --> 00:35:19,360
I have no particular strengths.

526
00:35:20,760 --> 00:35:21,960
Fortunately, I am frail.

527
00:35:23,230 --> 00:35:24,360
When I become emperor,

528
00:35:25,360 --> 00:35:26,630
if you find me to be in your way,

529
00:35:27,670 --> 00:35:28,590
I can die early.

530
00:35:39,320 --> 00:35:40,030
Your Highness,

531
00:35:41,800 --> 00:35:43,110
I do not love you.

532
00:35:44,448 --> 00:35:45,880
But I want to join forces with you

533
00:35:46,320 --> 00:35:47,190
to form an alliance.

534
00:35:53,400 --> 00:35:54,670
You are quite frank.

535
00:35:55,670 --> 00:35:56,760
If you are willing,

536
00:35:57,110 --> 00:35:58,150
we shall marry.

537
00:35:59,150 --> 00:36:01,000
From now on, we will rely on each other

538
00:36:01,280 --> 00:36:02,360
and face all storms together.

539
00:36:03,510 --> 00:36:04,510
If you do not betray me,

540
00:36:04,510 --> 00:36:05,510
I will never leave you.

541
00:36:06,176 --> 00:36:08,288
But I don't want
to just join forces with you.

542
